`8Keywords``   : Weapon_Dam
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

The maximum amount of damage that a weapon may be with or without quest point
enhancements is 40.  If you are in possession of a weapon that is of low level
and you wish to use quest points to enhance the weapon the level or your weapon
will raise in a 5 to 2 ratio. 

    example:		No enhancement	- level 25, average damage 24	       
 One enhancement  - level 27, average damage 29 	 Two enhancements -
level 29, average damage 34

